<plot>Based on the true story of the New London Lighthouse Haunting. Ernie loves his job on the local lighthouse, but his wife suffers from a deep loneliness. His love for work drives Amy to another man. Ernie is destroyed by the news and takes his life, leaving Amy and his friends behind. Or does he...? Amy beings to experience weird events during the night, at moments catching a glimpse of Ernie in the corner of her eye. She's heartbroken but needs to move on, however, a certain 'presence' won't let her.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?151071</url></doc>
